{"tid":2338640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歡迎嚟到平行宇宙","createTime":"2020-12-24T06:45:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T16:12:42.000Z","uid":86509,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5dfb01993c085768ba26f8512fd019769ae3acf9","tid":2338640,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T06:45:39.000Z","msg":"大家有冇諗過平行宇宙會係點樣？<br />\n但原來平行宇宙就係呢度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>連登</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n等我帶大家睇下呢個神秘世界同我哋有咩唔同<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDonki係藍店<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人要杯葛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n世界未日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OfnLjsa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOfnLjsa.jpg&h=e21e0dee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n侵係唔反共<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n侵只係商家佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hRyKz3X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhRyKz3X.jpg&h=bf728306&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最恐怖連館長都唔反共<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好難想像<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aeT26ct.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaeT26ct.jpg&h=30d2f010&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳秋實係大外宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到好多人黃變藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oLkAGLY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoLkAGLY.jpg&h=e86fad59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n艾未未係無立場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都叫好啲<br />\n好彩唔係藍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/35KmCmy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F35KmCmy.jpg&h=295013a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n棄保潛逃原來可以凍結財產<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_p.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_y.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZLzNxWN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZLzNxWN.jpg&h=024ceffe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國總統死咗，國務卿接任<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔同我哋宇宙係副總統接任<br />\n咁易被你估到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DFU9Mhf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDFU9Mhf.jpg&h=7d47dc51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後大絕<br />\n連登係支那零一產品<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已經震驚到唔知講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DAv5jAu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDAv5jAu.jpg&h=14665b5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n整個po大家輕鬆下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好屌我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4f11b87d7d0bc74dde144ddb9c9dbecd0bd7d4e","tid":2338640,"uid":86509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T06:51:35.000Z","msg":"平安夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個個去咗拍拖<br />\n係咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66a088d3586f5f6e17288de512537d8c9ed072f3","tid":2338640,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T06:54:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />召喚人"},{"pid":"9b80b5238b96ff0ec0ee6a8dbba07556142a0b17","tid":2338640,"uid":369151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T06:54:21.000Z","msg":"鬼有拖拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個個都拍拖唔通個個都想拍拖咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76d4a27bbe2bb861e220cc20fc48d6072a4276fe","tid":2338640,"uid":49016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T07:16:05.000Z","msg":"希望平行世界既我今晚有得屌女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0078a5374ffa7634a12fb5eadbcf87d96483b0bd","tid":2338640,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:12:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca49a9f1d4f996716eec76c629117124b68c4a7d","tid":2338640,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:35:13.000Z","msg":"膠po冇人理<br />\n連登己死<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f992ac0f4a7fd006367551199bf778a1236ed7